ENDPOINTS

[] POST   /pokebag/              → capturar/adicionar um Pokémon
[] GET    /pokebag/              → listar todos os Pokémon da bag
[] GET    /pokebag/{id}/         → ver detalhes de um Pokémon
[] PUT    /pokebag/{id}/         → upar / editar o Pokémon
[] DELETE /pokebag/{id}/         → soltar / deletar o Pokémon